latestIgtvVideos.title: an amazing scuba diving experience with @aqua_nomad .
latestIgtvVideos.caption: I remember when I was a kid I used to watch discovery channel with my dad and get scared of the big sharks and unusual fishes in the deep sea . I never imagined one day I'll be going in the deep sea and get a a chance to swim with this tiny little cute and friendly creatures ....since childhood I've always wondered what's in the sea are there only deadly and dangerous creatures and not any cute .!? but found my answer after this experience and unknowingly I fell in love with sea too....❤️
